📌 Problem Statement												
									
Businesses often track sales performance, but high revenue does not always translate into high profitability.									
The challenge is to identify which products, regions, and time periods are truly driving profit, and where the business may be losing margin despite strong sales.																
This dashboard aims to analyze sales and profit data to uncover key trends, highlight underperforming areas, and support data-driven decision-making.									
																		
❓ Key Questions This Dashboard Answers									
																	
📊 Performance Overview									
									
What are the total sales and total profit?									
How has profit changed over the years?																
									
🧩 Category & Sub-category Analysis									
									
Which categories generate the highest profit?									
Which sub-categories have high sales but low profit?									
What are the top-performing sub-categories?									
																		
🌍 Regional Insights									
									
Which states or regions contribute the most to sales?									
Are there regions with strong sales but weak profitability?						
									
📅 Time-Based Trends									
									
How do sales vary across months?									
Are there seasonal patterns in sales performance?									
																											
👤 Customer Insights			

Who are the most profitable customers?									
Is revenue concentrated among a few customers?									

“The goal is not just to visualize data, but to identify actionable insights that can improve profitability and business performance.”									
